{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations/task-107","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 107","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">obsession</span> je mesto gde ne možete prestati da razmišljate o nečemu jer ga toliko volite. Na primer, ako volite da igrate neku određenu video igru svaki dan, možete reći, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">This game is my obsession!</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Drones</span> su male letelice kojima se upravlja daljinskim upravljačem. Ljudi ih koriste za snimanje iz vazduha, trke ili jednostavno iz zabave. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I flew my drone over the park to get a great view from above.</span></p>\n</section>","instructions":"","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-have-a-conversation-about-preferences-and-motivations/task-107"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>But you know what my BLANK is BLANK days? BLANK!</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"obsession","feedback":"<p>Ova imenica opisuje nešto o čemu stalno razmišljate jer vam se veoma dopada.</p>"},{"answer":"these","feedback":"<p>Ova reč se koristi za govor o trenutnom periodu ili ovim danima. To je množina od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">this</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"Drones","feedback":"<p>Ova imenica odnosi se na letelice kojima se upravlja daljinski, a koje se često koriste za fotografisanje, trke ili zabavu. Reč počinje velikim slovom.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-boardroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Bob","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z